name: DescribeTabSetResult

methods.name: getDescription
methods.description: Returns the display description for the standard or custom app.

methods.name: getLabel
methods.description: Returns the display label for the standard or custom app.

methods.name: getLogoUrl
methods.description: Returns a fully qualified URL to the logo image associated with the standard or custom app.

methods.name: getNamespace
methods.description: Returns the developer namespace prefix of a Salesforce AppExchange managed package.

methods.name: getTabs
methods.description: Returns metadata information about the standard or custom app’s displayed tabs.

methods.name: isSelected
methods.description: Returns true if this standard or custom app is the user’s currently selected app. Otherwise, returns false.

description: Contains metadata information about a standard or custom app available in the Salesforce user interface.
